{"tid":1384546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水炮車三月出動用埋染料","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:10:05.000Z","uid":282208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd900fdd98258501b7ad5f59ccdd7b0ad2cf2ab","tid":1384546,"uid":282208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"無知一問，如果真係用埋染料可以點樣洗得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方近日驅散示威者所用的武力正不斷升級，消息稱警方斥資近2千萬元的三輛水炮車，據報已完成演練。《南華早報》今日更報道，指水炮車最快下月（8月）可出動驅散示威者。消息透露，水炮車將會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向示威者噴射液體染料</span></span>，除了為驅散大量的示威者，也為方便警方拘人。<br />\n<br />\n該三輛俗稱「水炮車」的人群管理特別用途車，耗資1,660萬元。本年4月已經「亮相」，保安局向立法會遞交的文件附上水炮車的外貌照片，可見車身配備兩個車頂噴水裝置、360 度攝錄鏡頭、水箱及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">催淚溶劑儲水缸</span></span>等設施。"},{"pid":"caaa0be275c204971053886f2682c0422a7a6847","tid":1384546,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"保鮮紙包全身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a597f00f38ccb1c774f62e292c9c92793c24108d","tid":1384546,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"b99af43f0e20c3a50f54f6ce3207a0e5a43edc7e","tid":1384546,"uid":282208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caaa0be275c204971053886f2682c0422a7a6847","tid":1384546,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"保鮮紙包全身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02: